description:
Download Warhammer 40.000: Tacticus for free and enjoy a tactical Warhammer game wherever you are: https://play.tacticusgame.com/squidmar
Use the code: SQUIDMARGEDDON to get some in game freebies!

This week, we spent 200 hours, painting $2000 worth of warhammer 40k Orks. All just to give it away to a stranger who had his entire collection stolen.

Wet Palette, Airbrush and 3 paint sets!?!? Yes, you can sign up to our waitlist here: https://harderairbrush.com/pages/squidmar-pre-launch
